name: "Everything and Anything" (UAP)
description:
Digital Art by United Architects of the Philippines Representative, Rebecca Vanessa Rellosa

The pandemic has accelerated changes in our behavior, such as working from home, global economies and digitization. 
With this enormous body of knowledge that can be reached at the touch of our fingertips, architects can possibly use this to the advantage of humanity, and revolutionize change the way we think and design.
